 />\n正如有人鍾意買股票有人鍾意放銀行<br />\n跳傘、潛水都危險架<br />\n<br />\n總知咁大個人自己衡量過承受到個風險<br />\n得到嘅快樂又冇其他低風險嘅活動可以取代咪去馬囉"},{"pid":"43e0dcc4cf88d9c2dc58972a41b6f96b6fd92079","tid":812271,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"唔安全<br />\n利申日日揸 見盡香港人揸車係幾咁on9"},{"pid":"415eb7fe95d8b617a5fe2196c6ec185c03bd1dbe","tid":812271,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"唔安全，但唔係完全唔可以控制，<br />\n自己駕駛態度同風格非常重要，<br />\n你下下死衝，逢窿必zip嘅十條命都唔夠死<br />\n安全車速車距，留意天氣，避免喺人地盲點，路口預計有盲毛隨時衝上，隨時有人平排cut鳩你，急停一定打死火燈<br />\n預多啲空間反應，已經安全好多"},{"pid":"107e8f672bd3bdc8026474c22e8c8d6f9dcc1891","tid":812271,"uid":96482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"唔安全，唔係對自己冇信心，係對馬路炸彈冇信心"},{"pid":"5e37ff3b223dd9125b9bbf82debd65e57b7eb0dd","tid":812271,"uid":16284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"唔安全，炒過，照渣<br />\n<br />\n睇你個人受到幾大風險，但渣26 既感覺，由其係棍電，係好難搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fa7cd820f1a3b64c27b76fc30f797652821374","tid":812271,"uid":169435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"比起26<br />\n單車先係真正玩命"},{"pid":"36e60c83e0dcd62e23341e03256abe7b6ec158b2","tid":812271,"uid":73504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:52:36.000Z","msg":"唔諗就無乜野，仲覺得幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但一諗到其他車可能會一野炒埋黎，就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就咁玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：揸緊26，因為驚，所以啱啱買左46"},{"pid":"340ce3ac26febefeeb5524452ebfb8364654b4a9","tid":812271,"uid":207373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e37ff3b223dd9125b9bbf8